erfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506103}, {"id": 311077, "content": "因为看了请回答1988喜欢上了吃拉面，还一定要用锅吃的那种。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1503824}, {"id": 311589, "content": "因为火蓝刀锋喜欢上军人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506096}, {"id": 311079, "content": "看了生活大爆炸，开始收藏漫画了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348067}, {"id": 311336, "content": "看《世界第一初恋》从此入坑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1504401}, {"id": 311337, "content": "被朋友安利各种奇奇怪怪的番后，开始喜欢美丽的nai子和萝莉，嗯…我是女的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352401}, {"id": 311083, "content": "小学二年级看了《金粉世家》，喜欢上了撩妹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107293}, {"id": 311084, "content": "我上铺说，小时候是看了神笔马良后决定学国画的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653216}, {"id": 311085, "content": "看了《秦时明月》后爱上历史", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485666}, {"id": 311086, "content": "因为看《日常》而喜欢吨吨吨的喝牛奶。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276616}, {"id": 311854, "content": "看了《漂亮的她》剪了和女二号一样的超短发，奈何长相差距有点大，剪完就悲剧了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508141}, {"id": 311343, "content": "看完半泽直树后想要做追债人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 887136}, {"id": 311601, "content": "因为看了《可惜不是你》\n所以最后选择当一名美术生\n想考中国美术学院💫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506197}, {"id": 311091, "content": "看了网球王子，有了打网球冲动。才发现那都是扯淡(　｀皿´)哼!!", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1503864}, {"id": 311093, "content": "目前还没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455228}, {"id": 311094, "content": "神盾局特工 想做特工 哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select